     Our Researchers
     Researchers at TFHRC are dedicated to finding innovative solutions
     to the problems facing the highway community today. Our advanced
     research and development apply new highway technologies to complex
     issues through the development of more economical, environmentally
     sensitive designs; more efficient, quality-controlled construction
     practices; and more durable products. The end result is a safer,
     more reliable highway transportation system. The research is
     conducted by the:
     Office of Safety Research & Development
     Office of Operations Research & Development
     Office of Infrastructure Research & Development.
     .................

